%20said%20he%20would%20revive%20the%20social%20media%20app's%20access%20in%20the%20United%20States%20when%20he%20returns%20to%20power%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Chinese%20social%20media%20app%20also%20thanked%20Mr%20Trump%20for%20%26quot%3Bproviding%20the%20necessary%20clarity%20and%20assurance%26quot%3B%2C%20hours%20after%20TikTok%20was%20forced%20to%20suspend%20its%20operations%20in%20the%20US%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20ban%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20agreement%20with%20our%20service%20providers%2C%20TikTok%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20restoring%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bytedance-owned%20app%20said%20in%20the%20earlier%20statement%2C%20while%20it%20also%20thanked%20the%20US%20President-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thank%20President%20Trump%20for%20providing%20the%20necessary%20clarity%20and%20assurance%20to%20our%20service%20providers%20that%20they%20will%20face%20no%20penalties%20providing%20TikTok%20to%20over%20170%20million%20Americans%20and%20allowing%20over%207%20million%20small%20businesses%20to%20thrive.%20It's%20a%20strong%20stand%20for%20the%20First%20Amendment%20and%20against%20arbitrary%20censorship.%20We%20will%20work%20with%20President%20Trump%20on%20a%20long-term%20solution%20that%20keeps%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20message%20to%20its%20users%2C%20TikTok%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20President%20Trump's%20efforts%2C%20TikTok%20is%20back%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20praise%20for%20the%20Republican%20came%20after%20Donald%20Trump%20took%20to%20his%20Truth%20Social%20and%20said%20he%20is%20planning%20to%20issue%20an%20executive%20order%20after%20taking%20over%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20US%20to%20delay%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20TikTok%20ban%20for%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20would%20%26quot%3Bextend%20the%20period%20of%20time%20before%20the%20law's%20prohibitions%20take%20effect%2C%20so%20that%20we%20can%20make%20a%20deal%20to%20protect%20our%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20the%20United%20States%20to%20have%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20ownership%20position%20in%20a%20joint%20venture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20said%20the%20executive%20order%20would%20specify%20there%20would%20be%20no%20liability%20for%20any%20company%20that%20helped%20keep%20TikTok%20from%20going%20dark%20before%20his%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20ahead%20of%20his%20inauguration%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20on%20Sunday%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrankly%2C%20we%20have%20no%20choice.%20We%20have%20to%20save%20it%26quot%3B.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20US%20will%20seek%20a%20joint%20venture%20to%20restore%20the%20short-video%20sharing%20app%20used%20by%20170%20million%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20stopped%20working%20for%20American%20users%20late%20on%20Saturday%20before%20a%20law%20shutting%20it%20down%20on%20national%20security%20grounds%20took%20effect%20on%20Sunday.%20US%20officials%20had%20warned%20that%20under%20Chinese%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%2C%20there%20was%20a%20risk%20of%20Americans'%20data%20being%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20had%20earlier%20said%20he%20would%20most%20likely%20give%20TikTok%20a%2090-day%20reprieve%20from%20the%20ban%20after%20he%20takes%20office%2C%20a%20promise%20TikTok%20cited%20in%20a%20notice%20posted%20to%20users%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Republican%20leader's%20stance%20to%20save%C2%A0TikTok%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20his%20first%20term%20in%20office.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20aimed%20to%20ban%20the%20app%20over%20concerns%20the%20company%20was%20sharing%20Americans'%20personal%20info%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government.%20More%20recently%2C%20Trump%20has%20said%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20warm%20spot%20in%20m