arathon%20might%20be%20a%20better%20move%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20her%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20had%20already%20scaled%20down%20her%20TikTok%20screentime%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20creator%20engaging%20with%20other%20creators%2C%20whether%20they're%20mutuals%20of%20mine%20or%20not%2C%20there's%20this%20underlying%20level%20of%20comparison.%20What%20is%20their%20engagement%3F%20What%20are%20their%20views%3F%20What%20are%20their%20likes%3F%20And%20so%20it%20wasn't%20really%20just%20this%20reprieve%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20also%20this%20breeding%20ground%20for%20me%20to%20see%20what%20everyone%20else%20doing%20and%20then%20compare%20myself%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20have%20filled%20my%20time%20in%20other%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244a4a1f3-d382-4815-81e5-4540f80ceda1%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20of%20magic%20in%20a%20bottle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20people%20might%20rethink%20their%20social%20media%20habits%2C%20the%20majority%20will%20likely%20focus%20on%20finding%20an%20adequate%20substitute%20(at%20least%20until%20TikTok%20figures%20out%20its%20future)%2C%20Charles%20Lindsey%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20the%20University%20at%20Buffalo's%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20there's%20industry%20change%20for%20regulatory%20or%20competitive%20reasons%2C%20%26quot%3Bsometimes%20you'll%20see%20a%20certain%20percentage%20of%20people%20that%20will%20say%2C%20'You%20know%20what%3F%20I'm%20going%20to%20take%20this%20time%20to%20reflect%20and%20unplug%20before%20I%20decide%20what%20to%20do%20next.'%20And%20that's%20certainly%20a%20valid%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20users%20would%20still%20end%20up%20migrating%20to%20other%20apps%20if%20they%20haven't%20already%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20this%20photo%20illustration%20an%20iPhone%20displays%20a%20popup%20message%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20TikTok%20on%20January%2019%2C%202025%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678d64dfae09223df2baa2b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETikTok%20was%20briefly%20unavailable%20for%20US%20users%20overnight%20on%20Saturday.%3Cp%3Eillustration%20by%20Kayla%20Bartkowski%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20race%20is%20on%20to%20see%20which%20app%20can%20absorb%20wayward%20TikTok%20users%2C%20whether%20that's%20RedNote%20or%20Lemon8%2C%20Meta%20platforms%2C%20X%2C%20or%20YouTube.%20There's%20also%20a%20possibility%20that%20other%20apps%20emerge%20to%20fill%20the%20void%2C%20Lindsey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20users%20and%20content%20creators%2C%20it%20really%20boils%20down%20to%20dollars%20and%20cents%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20whichever%20platform%20makes%20the%20most%20sense%20in%20terms%20of%20pushing%20out%20their%20content%2C%20developing%20a%20critical%20mass%20of%20followers%2C%20and%20getting%20their%20existing%20followers%20to%20migrate%20over%20and%20so%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20TikTok%20ban%20brought%20on%20a%20distinct%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-users-angry-mark-zuckerberg-meta-instragram-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupswing%20in%20Mark%20Zuckerberg-hate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20promises%20to%20boycott%20his%20apps%2C%20outrage%20alone%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20move%20the%20needle%20on%20which%20app%20ultimately%20fills%20the%20void.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20can%20have%20a%20preference%2C%20and%20we're%20seeing%20that%20with%20RedNote%20shooting%20up%20to%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20that%20then%20becomes%20the%20app%20of%20choice%20three%2C%20six%20months%2C%20a%20year%20down%20the%20road%2C%20I%20think%20it%20all%20boils%20down%20to%20the%20functionality%20of%20the%20app.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20also%20come%20down%20to%20mimicking%20the%20magic-in-a-bottle%20that%20was%20the%20TikTok%20experience%2C%20which%20had%20a%20unique%20rise%20to%20popularity%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20a%20subsequent%20five-year%20reign%2C%20Lewis%20said.%20TikTok%20had%20an%20%26quot%3Bunbeatable%26quot%3B%20algorithm%20and%20comment%20sections%20that%20kept%20users%20entertained%20and%20engaged%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20they%20have%20to%20search%20too%20hard%20for%20a%20suitable%20alternative%2C%20then%20they%20will%20reevaluate%20their%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20said.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20aren't%20lazy%2C%20but%20they%20aren't%20going%20to%20jump%20through%20hoops%20in%20order%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20waste%20time%20on%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-doom-scrolling-rednote-instagram-facebook-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737327040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678d6431ae09223df2baa2a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-doom-scrolling-rednote-instagram-facebook-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Instead%20of%20following%20the%20masses%20to%20TikTok%20replicas%20like%20RedNote%20or%20Lemon8%2C%20some%20users%20say%20they%20would%20ditch%20doomscrolling%20culture%20for%20good.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbalevic%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Balevic%2CJordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A110%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-doom-scrolling-rednote-instagram-facebook-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2