3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-back-online-us-shutdown-biden-trump-media-app-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegan%20coming%20back%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-trump-executive-order-ban-app-restore-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20would%20issue%20an%20executive%20order%20extending%20the%20deadline%20for%20TikTok%20to%20find%20a%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20current%20users%20can%20access%20TikTok%2C%20the%20social%20media%20app%20and%20other%20ones%20owned%20by%20ByteDance%20are%20still%20not%20available%20in%20app%20stores.%20That%20includes%20video%20editing%20app%20Cap%20Cut%2C%20social%20media%20app%20Lemon8%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20who%20tried%20to%20log%20into%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%20were%20met%20with%20a%20similar%20message%20to%20the%20one%20that%20for%20several%20hours%20greeted%20users%20on%20TikTok.%20The%20message%20says%20that%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20is%20currently%20%26quot%3Bnot%20available%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20law%20was%20enacted%20that%20banned%20the%20app%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRest%20assured%20we're%20working%20to%20restore%20our%20service%20in%20the%20US.%20Please%20stay%20tuned!%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20says.%20In%20a%20since%20deleted%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20developers%20said%20on%20X%20that%20they%20were%20not%20told%20the%20app%20would%20shut%20down%20before%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20MARVEL%20SNAP%20is%20temporarily%20unavailable%20in%20US%20app%20stores%20and%20is%20unavailable%20to%20play%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20outage%20is%20a%20surprise%20to%20us%20and%20wasn't%20planned.%20MARVEL%20SNAP%20isn't%20going%20anywhere.%20We're%20actively%20working%20on%20getting%20the%20game%20up%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20will%20update%20you%20once%20we%20have%20more%20to%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20isn't%20the%20only%20popular%20Marvel%20game%20owned%20and%20created%20by%20a%20large%20Chinese%20developer.%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Rivals%2C%26quot%3B%20developed%20by%20Chinese%20company%20NetEase%2C%20was%20released%20in%20December%20to%20massive%20player%20numbers%20across%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarvel%20Rivals%26quot%3B%20hit%20a%20peak%20player%20count%20of%20over%20640%2C000%20on%20Steam%2C%20the%20PC%20game%20store%2C%20this%20month%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20one%20of%20the%20top%20games%20in%20the%20PlayStation%20and%20Xbox%20stores%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20TikTok%20and%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20ban%20was%20to%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Rivals%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMarvel%20Snap%26quot%3B%20participated%20in%20collaborative%20events%2C%20which%20required%20users%20to%20log%20in%20to%20their%20accounts%20on%20each%20game%2C%20sharing%20account%20information%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarvel%20Rivals%26quot%3B%20also%20participated%20in%20similar%20events%20in%20December%20with%20%26quot%3BFortnite%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20American%20developer%20Epic%20Games.%20Tencent%2C%20another%20Chinese%20gaming%20mega-corporation%2C%20owns%20about%2029%25%20of%20Epic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%20has%20a%20strong%20footing%20in%20the%20US%20games%20industry.%20It%20owns%20100%25%20of%20Riot%20Games%2C%20which%20makes%20%26quot%3BLeague%20of%20Legends%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BValorant%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20significant%20investments%20in%20the%20makers%20of%20%26quot%3BClash%20of%20Clans%2C%26quot%3B%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20companies%20like%20NetEase%20and%20Tencent%20don't%20have%20a%20specific%20%26quot%3Bapp%2C%26quot%3B%20laws%20like%20the%20one%20targeting%20ByteDance%20could%20ultimately%20lead%20to%20scrutiny%20of%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20US%20games%20industry%2C%20games%20YouTuber%20and%20analyst%20Paul%20Tassi%20wrote%20in%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20claim%20here%20could%20be%20that%20Tencent%20being%20intimately%20involved%20with%20loads%20of%20major%20games%20that%20US%20citizens%2C%20and%20particularly%20children%2C%20are%20playing%20might%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bharmful%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20influence%2C%20or%20something%20along%20those%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20Tassi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarvel%20Studios%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarvel-snap-removed-from-us-app-stores-tiktok-ban-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737316416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678d4762ae09223df2baa234%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarvel-snap-removed-from-us-app-stores-tiktok-ban-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Popular%20mobile%20game%20'Marvel%20Snap'%20went%20offline%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20TikTok%20ban.%20Snap%20isn't%20the%20only%20popular%20Marvel%20game%20owned%20by%20a%20large%20Chinese%20developer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarvel-snap-removed-from-us-app-stores-tiktok-ban-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dramatic%20day%20ushers%20in%20a%20fragile%20Israel-Hamas%20ceasefire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737316298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_new