n%20the%20media%20before%20the%20star%20athlete%20himself%20made%20the%20surprising%20announcement.%20Neeraj%20scripted%20history%20for%20India%20during%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%202020%20by%20clinching%20a%20gold%20medal%20in%20javelin%20throw.%20He%20became%20the%20first-ever%20track%20and%20field%20athlete%20from%20the%20nation%20to%20win%20the%20top%20honour%20in%20an%20individual%20event.%20Neeraj%20then%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20a%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%20following%20edition%20of%20the%20quadrennial%20event%20that%20was%20held%20in%20Paris%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20exclusive%20details%20from%20Neeraj's%20private%20ceremony%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20It%20was%20a%20destination%20wedding%20for%20Neeraj%20and%20Himani%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Himachal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20The%20functions%20for%20the%20same%20were%20on%2014%2C%2015%20and%2016th%20January%20this%20year%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Around%2040%20to%2050%20people%20were%20the%20part%20of%20the%20private%20ceremony%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20After%20the%20marriage%2C%20both%20Neeraj%20and%20Himani%20went%20to%20foreign%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20When%20the%20couple%20returns%20to%20India%2C%20a%20reception%20will%20take%20place%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Himani%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20a%20course%20related%20to%20sports%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Neeraj%20was%20named%20the%20best%20male%20javelin%20thrower%20in%20the%20world%20in%202024%20by%20globally-renowned%20American%20magazine%20'Track%20and%20Field%20News'.%20The%2027-year-old%20Chopra%20pipped%20two-time%20world%20champion%20Anderson%20Peters%20of%20Grenada%20for%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%202024%20rankings%20published%20by%20the%20California-based%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20was%20also%20the%20top-ranker%20in%20the%20men's%20javelin%20throw%20rankings%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E