quot%3B%20the%20WEF%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20India's%20target%20of%20becoming%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%20is%20realistic%2C%20Mr%20Brende%20said%20India%20will%20be%20a%20%2410%20trillion%20economy%20soon%2C%20and%20what%20also%20works%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20India%20is%20that%20trade%20is%20now%20pivoting%20more%20towards%20digital%20trade%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20growing%20three%20times%20faster%20than%20traditional%20goods.%20And%20these%20are%20areas%20where%20India%20is%20very%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20by%20NDTV%20on%20some%20of%20the%20key%20challenges%20or%20opportunities%20that%20come%20with%20greater%20digitalisation%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20Mr%20Brende%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20increased%20productivity.%20And%20productivity%20is%20like%20producing%20more%20with%20less%20resources.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20this%20will%20challenge%20some%20jobs%20that%20are%20back%20offices%20today%20or%20other%20jobs.%20But%20if%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20people%20moving%20into%20areas%20where%20you%20produce%20higher%20up%20in%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20you%20can%20pay%20better%2C%20you%20can%20produce%20more.%20And%20that's%20prosperity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20for%20India%2C%20there%20are%20of%20course%20huge%20opportunities%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20new%20technologies.%20But%20short%20term%2C%20it%20also%20creates%20challenges%20because%20one%20has%20to%20upskill%20and%20reskill%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WEF%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate%20Agenda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20world%20grappling%20to%20stick%20to%20the%201.5%20degree%20Celsius%20or%20below%20mark%2C%20the%20WEF%20has%20integrated%20climate%20as%20a%20primary%20driver%20in%20its%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20%5Bclimate%5D%20incredibly%20important.%20And%20I%20think%20you%20just%20came%20back%20from%20Los%20Angeles.%20You%20saw%20the%20wildfires.%20We%20have%20seen%20droughts.%20We%20know%20that%20agriculture%20production%2C%20production%20of%20food%20is%20being%20more%20challenged%20now%20because%20there%20are%20areas%20where%20you%20can't%20just%20grow%20what%20you%20used%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20in%20general%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20inaction%20far%20exceeds%20the%20cost%20of%20action%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20climate%20change.%20So%20we%20need%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20momentum.%20We%20will%20need%20to%20emit%20less%20CO2%20(carbon%20dioxide)%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%20to%20even%20be%20able%20to%20stick%20to%20a%202%20degree%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Brende%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%202%20degree%20target%20means%20a%20lot%2C%20especially%20to%20countries%20that%20are%20most%20vulnerable%2C%20which%20happen%20to%20be%20countries%20that%20have%20emitted%20the%20least%20CO2%2C%20traditionally%20being%20African%20countries%2C%20but%20also%20including%20India%20that%20has%20already%20seen%20heat%20waves%20and%20%26quot%3Bseen%20the%20cost%20of%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-day%20meeting%20at%20Davos%20beginning%20Monday%20will%20explore%20how%20to%20re-launch%20growth%2C%20harness%20new%20technologies%20and%20strengthen%20social%20and%20economic%20resilience%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum.%20The%20global%20meeting%20will%20see%20participation%20by%20nearly%203%2C000%20leaders%20from%20over%20130%20countries%2C%20including%20350%20governmental%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20participation%20at%20Davos%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20partnerships%2C%20attract%20investment%2C%20and%20position%20the%20country%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20sustainable%20development%20and%20technological%20innovation.%20India%20is%20sending%20five%20Union%20ministers%2C%20three%20chief%20ministers%2C%20and%20ministers%20from%20several