20it's%20all%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20year%20of%20real%20crisis%20around%20the%20world%2C%20whether%20it's%20conflict%2C%20concerns%20over%20sustainable%20development%2C%20and%20concerns%20over%20so%20many%20issues%2C%20not%20least%20of%20all%20the%20future%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20and%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENuclear%20Fusion%20Energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mumgaard%20began%20by%20giving%20an%20overview%20of%20the%20future%20of%20nuclear%20plants%20in%20terms%20of%20fusion%20energy%20and%20safe%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20completely%20different%20from%20existing%20nuclear%20power.%20It's%20the%20opposite.%20In%20fusion%2C%20you're%20combining%20light%20elements%20to%20make%20heavier%20ones%20the%20same%20way%20the%20Sun%20works.%20That%20means%20that%20there's%20no%20meltdown%2C%20there's%20no%20connection%20to%20weapons%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20long-lived%20nuclear%20waste%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mumgaard%2C%20who%20is%20dealing%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20aspects%20of%20clean%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20right%20now%20is%20we%20still%20have%20to%20develop%20the%20technology%20and%20deploy%20it.%20We're%20building%20on%20the%20very%20first%20power%20plants%20right%20now.%20Right%20now%2C%20we're%20about%20halfway%20through%20building%20the%20first%20prototype%20outside%20of%20Boston%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mumgaard%20said%20his%20company%20spun%20out%20of%20MIT%20(Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20about%20three%20years%20ago%20building%20this%20machine.%20In%20about%20two%20years%2C%20we'll%20turn%20the%20machine%20on%2C%20and%20that'll%20be%20an%20important%20point%20in%20the%20world%20where%20we'll%20have%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20industrial-scale%20fusion%20power%20being%20created%20by%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Commonwealth%20Fusion%20Systems%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20matters%20of%20cost%2C%20which%20will%20be%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20producing%20clean%20energy%2C%20Mr%20Mumgaard%20said%20the%20goal%20with%20all%20new%20sustainable%20energy%20is%20to%20produce%20energy%20in%20a%20way%20that%20the%20world%20can%20enable%20growth%2C%20which%20means%20it%20has%20to%20be%20low%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20one%20of%20the%20great%20things%20about%20technologies%20like%20fusion%20is%20you're%20using%20all%20these%20other%20technologies%20that%20have%20come%20before%2C%20you're%20adding%20them%20up.%20And%20so%20you're%20getting%20the%20cost%20advantages%20that%20came%20from%20new%20ways%20to%20manufacture%2C%20you're%20getting%20cost%20advantages%20that%20come%20from%20simulation%20and%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20fusion%20itself.%20And%20so%20we%20think%20that%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20low-cost%20energy%20source.%20We%20need%20to%20still%20build%20this%20and%20have%20the%20receipts.%20And%20that's%20what%20we're%20working%20on%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20And%20Workplace%20Disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Awadhiya%20of%20SimpliAI%20said%20he%20strongly%20believes%20that%20AI%20will%20work%20in%20conjunction%20with%20humanity%20and%20workforce%20to%20elevate%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20our%20work%20is%20-%20while%20focused%20on%20automation%20at%20SimpliAI%20-%20we%20firmly%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20all%20of%20these%20AI%20tools%20are%20going%20to%20elevate%20the%20productivity%20of%20workforces%20across%20functions%20and%20across%20roles.%20It's%20very%20important%20for%20all%20the%20players%20to%20really%20make%20that%20argument%20very%20clear%2C%20very%20succinct%20to%20the%20people%20at%20large%2C%20so%20that%20the%20fear%20factor%20around%20AI%20is%20actually%20replaced%20with%20positivity%20and%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Awadhiya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20jobs%20disappearing%20due%20to%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20as%20the%20report%20of%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20itself%20states%20that%20while%20there'll%20be%20about%2090%20odd%20million%20jobs%20which%20will%20be%20substituted%20by%202030%2C%20but%20170%20million%20more%20would%20be%20created.%20So%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20it's%20like%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution.%20Jobs%20will%20get%20substituted%2C%20the%20jobs%20which%20are%20repetitive%2C%20low%20value%20in%20nature%2C%20with%20high-value%20jobs%20being%20moved%20up%20the%20value%20chain%20to%20people.%20And%20to%20me%2C%20that%20is%20what%20is%20going%20to%20unlock%20productivity%20for%20humanity%20at%20large.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20Of%20Education%20And%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvanti%20Fellows%20founder%20Akshay%20Saxena%20cautioned%20against%20going%20too%20fast%20with%20AI%20in%20the%20area%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20a%20couple%20of%20things%20to%20be%20really%20careful%20about%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20look%20at%20it%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20we%20already%20have%20massive%20inequity%20that's%20growing.%20One%20is%2C%20like%20Abhishek%20said%2C%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20will%20change%2C%20which%20means%20you'll%20have%20to%20almost%20work%20with%20an%20AI%20copilot%20alongside%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20our%20schools%20doing%20to%20equip%20kids%20to%20do%20that%3F%20And%20how%20many%20kids%20even%20have%20exposure%20to%20this%3F%20Because%20the%20majority%20of%20kids%20in%20India%20don't%20even%20have%20cell%20phones%20of%20their%20own%2C%20or%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20in%20any%20meaningful%20way.%20And%20what%20does%20that%20mean%20for%20our%20colleges%3F%20Because%20India%20has%20amongst%20the%20largest%20en