in%20May%202024.%20He%20had%20told%20us%20over%20the%20phone%20that%20he%20got%20injured%20in%20the%20war%20on%20May%209%2C%202024.%20Since%20then%20we%20haven't%20heard%20from%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20appealing%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%20so%20that%20his%20brother%20could%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20her%20son%2C%20Azharuddin%20Khan's%20mother%20Nasreen%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Azamgarh's%20Gulami%20Ka%20Pura%20area%2C%20breaks%20down%20into%20tears%20and%20recalls%20an%20agent's%20bait%20of%20a%20high-salary%20job%20that%20took%20his%20son%20away%20from%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20spoken%20to%20him%20for%20the%20last%20ten%20months%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20left%20with%20agent%20Vinod%20on%20January%2026%2C%202024.%20He%20had%20offered%20Azharuddin%20a%20job%20as%20a%20security%20guard.%20He%20said%20he%20will%20get%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzharuddin%20Khan%20-%20the%20primary%20earner%20in%20his%20family%20-%20was%20in%20regular%20touch%20with%20his%20family%20after%20he%20left.%20He%20told%20them%20he%20was%20being%20trained%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%201%2C%20his%20father%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20when%20he%20got%20to%20know%20that%20he%20had%20joined%20the%20Russian%20Army.%20Seven%20days%20later%2C%20on%20April%208%2C%20he%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20last%20conversation%20with%20my%20son%20was%20on%20April%2027.%20He%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'Amma%2C%20I%20will%20work%20here%20for%20six%20months%20and%20I%20will%20return%20home%20after%20that.%20I%20haven't%20heard%20from%20home%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20distraught%20Nasreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaiting%20For%20News%20On%20'Missing'%20Son%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Father%20of%20Humeshwar%20Prasad%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Sathiyaon%20town%2C%20also%20h