first%20phase%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20Israel%20had%20US%20support%20to%20return%20to%20the%20war%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%20City%2C%20well%20before%20the%20ceasefire%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20people%20were%20already%20celebrating%2C%20waving%20Palestinian%20flags%20in%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20warned%20Gaza%20residents%20early%20Sunday%20not%20to%20approach%20its%20forces%20or%20%26quot%3Bthe%20buffer%20zone%26quot%3B%20near%20Israeli%20territory%20%26quot%3Bfor%20your%20safety%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20the%20ceasefire%20was%20met%20with%20guarded%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20trust%20our%20side%20or%20their%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20taxi%20driver%20David%20Gutterman.%20%26quot%3BAlways%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20something%2C%20a%20problem%2C%20can%20pop%20up%2C%20but%20all%20in%20all%20I'm%20really%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShai%20Zaik%2C%20an%20employee%20at%20Tel%20Aviv's%20art%20museum%2C%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bmixed%20feelings%26quot%3B%20but%20was%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20hope%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20hostages%20would%20return%20after%20so%20many%20disappointments%20in%20the%20last%20year.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20prepared%20reception%20centres%20to%20provide%20medical%20treatment%20and%20counselling%20to%20the%20freed%20hostages%20before%20they%20return%20to%20their%20families.%20Health%20workers%20have%20warned%20of%20the%20psychological%20challenges%20the%20captives%20will%20face%20upon%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E600%20Trucks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgyptian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Badr%20Abdelatty%20said%20600%20trucks%20a%20day%20would%20enter%20Gaza%20after%20the%20ceasefire%20took%20effect%2C%20including%2050%20carrying%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war's%20only%20previous%20truce%2C%20for%20one%20week%20in%20November%202023%2C%20a