0value%20of%20cryptocurrencies%20like%20bitcoin%2C%20worth%20over%20%24100%2C000%20each%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20hedge%20against%20inflation%20or%20pay%20down%20the%20national%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20advancements%20in%20quantum%20computing%20could%20undermine%20that%20security%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20a%20whole%20lot%20more%20%E2%80%94%20two%20researchers%20on%20the%20advanced%20technology%20explained%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20talking%20about%20is%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hack%2C%20not%20just%20into%20individual%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20but%20our%20larger%20financial%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Arthur%20Herman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Quantum%20Alliance%20Initiative%20at%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuantum%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20technology%20that%20combines%20the%20disciplines%20of%20computer%20science%2C%20mathematics%2C%20and%20quantum%20mechanics%20to%20solve%20more%20complex%20problems%20more%20quickly%20than%20is%20possible%20through%20classical%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20classical%20computing%20uses%20binary%20digits%20%E2%80%94%C2%A00s%20and%201s%2C%20called%20bits%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20represent%20information%2C%20quantum%20computing%20relies%20on%20the%20quantum%20equivalent%20of%20bits%2C%20called%20qubits%2C%20which%20are%20represented%20by%20a%20superposition%20of%20multiple%20states%2C%20such%20as%200%2C%201%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQubits%20themselves%20are%20unstable%2C%20and%20it's%20difficult%20to%20predict%20their%20behavior.%20They%20behave%20differently%20when%20observed%2C%20making%20measuring%20their%20state%20challenging%2C%20and%20require%20specific%20conditions%20such%20as%20low%20light%20or%20extremely%20cold%20environments%20to%20replicate%20results%20reliably%20and%20without%20errors.%20The%20errors%20become%20especially%20pronounced%2C%20and%20the%20qubits%20behavior%20less%20reliable%2C%20when%20scaling%20the%20computing%20power%20up%20using%20additional%20qubits%20%E2%80%94%20making%20advancement%20in%20the%20field%20slowgoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20qubit's%20capacity%20to%20exist%20in%20multiple%20states%20at%20once%2C%20like%20a%20spinning%20coin%20appearing%20to%20show%20both%20heads%20and%20tails%20simultaneously%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eallows%20quantum%20computers%20to%20quickly%20calculate%20equations%20with%20multiple%20solutions%20and%20perform%20advanced%20computations%20that%20would%20be%20impossible%20for%20classical%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20the%20field%20agree%20that%20the%20previously%20unsolvable%20computations%20could%20help%20discover%20new%20drugs%2C%20develop%20new%20chemical%20compounds%2C%20break%20our%20current%20encryption%20methods%2C%20and%20reverse%20the%20pseudonymity%20of%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d67e4679-a253-4786-9d0d-c0bfecdd93eb%5C%22%3ESupercomputers%3A%2010%20septillion%20years%20behind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-unveiled-quantum-computer-chip-willow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20unveiled%20Willow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20new%20quantum%20chip%2C%20which%20represents%20a%20major%20advancement%20in%20commercial%20quantum%20computing.%20The%20company%20says%20Willow%20can%20perform%20a%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%2C%20an%20industry-accepted%20calculation%20used%20to%20measure%20the%20performance%20of%20quantum%20computers%2C%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20a%20task%20that%20would%20take%20the%20current%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%20to%20complete.%20That's%2010%20followed%20by%2024%20zeroes%2C%20a%20timeframe%20that%20exceeds%20the%20age%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillow%20also%20solves%20a%20challenge%20related%20to%20correcting%20errors%20in%20the%20qubits'%20behavior%20while%20scaling%20the%20computing%20power%20up%2C%20which%20has%20plagued%20the%20industry%20for%2030%20years.%20Other%20private%20companies%2C%20like%20IBM%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20allies%20like%20France%2C%20and%20adversaries%20including%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20are%20also%20working%20to%20develop%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarl%20Holmqvist%20has%20served%20as%20a%20quantum%20security%20advisor%20to%20major%20government%20bodies%2C%20including%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20and%20NATO.%20He%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Lastwall%2C%20which%20provides%20cybersecurity%20solutions%20designed%20to%20protect%20users%20from%20quantum%20computing%20threats.%20Holmqvist%20said%20that%20while%20the%20timeframe%20for%20creating%20a%20large%2C%20fully%20functional%20quantum%20computer%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20to%20the%20midsize%20versions%20with%20still%20unreliable%20qubit%20behavior%20we%20have%20now%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20unclear%2C%20the%20things%20such%20a%20device%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20when%20the%20technology%20becomes%20more%20stable%20are%20starting%20to%20come%20into%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20really%20concerning%20thing%20is%20that%2C%20right%20now%2C%20when%20we%20store%20personal%20information%2C%20we%20encrypt%20that%20data%2C%20and%20we%20often%20encrypt%20it%20with%20systems%20that%20use%20public%20key%20cryptography%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that's%20what%20quantum%20computers%20may%20come%20to%20actually%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmqvist%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20have%20to%20think%20of%20all%20the%20databases%20and%20all%20the%20systems%20that%20have%20records%20of%20what%20we%20do%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20for%20privacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20basic%20data%20privacy%20or%20the%20risk%20of%20personal%20financial%20details%20becoming%20public.%20Encrypted%20data%2C%20from%20national%20security%20secrets%20to%20the%20blockchain%20and%20beyond%2C%20will%20be%20readily%20accessible%20and%2C%20more%20worryingly%2C%20manipulatable%20by%20anyone%20with%20a%20quantum-capable%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20peeling%20back%20the%20layers%2C%20it's%20like%20anything%20that's%20internet-connected%20will%20likely%20have%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmqvist%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20trust%20that%20the%20links%20between%20systems%20are%20secure%20and%20the%20data%20that's%20gone%20between%20them%20is%20secure%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20get%20into%20those%20that%20they're%20encrypted.%20If%20you%20take%20away%20that%20default%20assumption%2C%20it%20allows%20so%20many%20new%20entry%20points%20into%20systems%20that%20it%20becomes%20quite%20concerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHerman%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Quantum%20Alliance%20Initiative%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20hack%20from%20a%20quantum%20computer%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Btotally%20stealth%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20a%20quantum%20machine's%20potential%20ability%20to%20lay%20bare%20encryption%20and%20operate%20inside%20computer%20systems%20without%20leaving%20a%20trace%2C%20meaning%20a%20bad%20actor%20could%20cause%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophic%26quot%3B%20damage%20without%20being%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20situation%20like%20with%20a%20conventional%20hacker%2C%20where%20he%20breaks%20into%20one%20system%2C%20into%20one%20bank%20or%20one%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20and%20then%20when%20he's%20finished%20with%20one%2C%20has%20to%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20Herman%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you've%20cracked%20one%20system%2C%20you've%20cracked%20them%20all%2C%20and%20you%20can%20help%20yourself%2C%20almost%20instantaneously%2C%20to%20whatever%20assets%20or%20moneys%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHerman%20said%20the%20race%20to%20achieve%20reliable%20quantum%20computing%20mirrors%20the%20nuclear%20arms%20race%2C%20but%20officials%20aren't%20taking%20the%20risk%20nearly%20as%20seriously%20as%20he%20thinks%20they%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20where%20we%20stand%20in%20our%20competition%20with%20Russia%20and%20particularly%20China%2C%20the%20race%20to%20a%20quantum%20computer%20should%20be%20one%20of%20the%20major%20factors%20and%20threats%20that%20we%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20deter%2C%26quot%3B%20Herman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20also%20a%20challenge%20that%20we%20want%20to%20come%20out%20on%20top%20of%20and%20be%20the%20first%20ones%20with%20a%20quantum%20computer%20because%2C%20ultimately%2C%20that'll%20be%20the%20real%20deterrence%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20threat%3A%20If%20you%20try%20to%20do%20it%20to%20us%2C%20then%20we%20can%20do%20it%20with%20even%20more%20devastating%20effect%20on%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737297241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678aebacae09223df2ba973c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Developments%20in%20quantum%20computing%20highlight%20the%20risk%20to%20financial%20institutions%20and%20national%20security%20if%20new%20encryption%20measures%20aren't%20developed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockcha