%20of%20donning%20the%20Indian%20jersey%20again%20after%20eight%20years%20was%20dashed%20when%20the%20national%20selectors%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20sat%20together%20to%20pick%20India's%20squads%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%20the%20ODIs%20against%20England.%20There%20was%20no%20place%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%20for%20the%2033-year-old%20Vidarbha%20captain%2C%20who%20even%20had%20an%20average%20of%20752%20before%20the%20final%20match%20of%20the%20domestic%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Nair%20exclusion%2C%20former%20India%20captain%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20pointed%20out%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20player%20failed%20to%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20should%20they%20fit%20him%3F%20You%20could%20have%20taken%20the%20spot%20of%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer.%20KL%20will%20perform%20the%20role%20of%20second%20wicetkeeper-batter%20for%20this%20team%20and%20his%20performance%20during%202023%20World%20Cup%20was%20good.%20I%20don't%20think%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20has%20played%20much%20ODI%20cricket%20after%20that.%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20has%20also%20performed%20well%20in%20the%20format.%20That%20is%20why%20Karun%20Nair%20has%20not%20been%20picked%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHLwovS3ABS0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESports%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20his%20form%20during%20Ranji%20Trophy%20remains%20same%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20hard%20for%20Team%20India%20to%20not%20pick%20him%20during%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20tour%20of%20England%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuous%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20BCCI%20about%20the%20relevance%20for%20scoring%20heavily%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20if%20a%20player%20does%20not%20get%20selected%20on%20that%20count%2C%20and%20about%20the%20honesty%20of%20the%20team%20management's%20decision%20to%20place%20significance%20on%20domestic%20matches.%20But%20in%20truth%2C%20as%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20explained%2C%20it%20was%20indeed%20tough%20to%20include%20Karun%20in%20a%20squad%20of%2015%20in%20the%20current%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20it%20is%20tough.%20Those%20are%20really%20special%20performances.%20I%20mean%2C%20someone%20who%20averages%20-%20700-plus%2C%20750-plus%20(before%20Vijay%20Hazare%20final).%20We%20did%20have%20a%20chat%20(about%20Karun)%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarkar%20said%20in%20the%20press%20meet%20to%20announce%20the%20Indian%20squads%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20in%20this%20team%20is%20very%20difficult.%20I%20mean%2C%20look%20at%20the%20guys%20who've%20been%20picked.%20All%20average%20well%20in%20excess%20of%20mid-40s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20you%20can't%20fit%20everyone%20in.%20It's%20a%20squad%20of%2015.%20But%20those%20performances%20(like%20Karun)%20certainly%20make%20you%20take%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737295980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fv118ruv8_karun-nair-x_625x300_12_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhere-should-they-sunil-gavaskar-on-karun-nair-being-overlooked-for-champions-trophy-7504995%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Out-of-favour%20India%20batter%20Karun%20Nair%20scored%20779%20runs%20across%208%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%20389.50%20in%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%202024-25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhere-should-they-sunil-gavaskar-on-karun-nair-being-overlooked-for-champions-trophy-7504995%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Soha%3A%