complex%20defamation%20lawsuit%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Canada's%20Anson%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Moez%20Kassam%20said%20his%20firm%20has%20shared%20research%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20sources%26quot%3B%20including%20Hindenburg's%20Nate%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Market%20Frauds%20portal%20said%20that%20court%20documents%20allegedly%20revealed%20that%20Hindenburg%20colluded%20with%20Anson%20while%20preparing%20a%20report.%20The%20preparation%20of%20bearish%20reports%20without%20disclosure%20of%20participation%20can%20be%20charged%20as%20securities%20fraud%20by%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20(SEC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20short%20sellers%20borrow%20a%20security%2C%20sell%20it%20on%20the%20open%20market%2C%20and%20expect%20to%20repurchase%20it%20for%20less%20money%20after%20their%20damning%20report%20against%20the%20company%20brings%20stock%20down%2C%20involvement%20of%20hedge%20funds%20raises%20eyebrows%20as%20they%20could%20also%20place%20parallel%20bets%2C%20putting%20more%20downward%20pressure%20on%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anson%20and%20Kassam%20couldn't%20be%20immediately%20reached%2C%20an%20email%20sent%20to%20Anderson%20remained%20unanswered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20for%20a%20fact%2C%20from%20the%20email%20conversations%20between%20Anderson%20and%20Anson%20Funds%2C%20that%20he%20was%20indeed%20working%20for%20Anson%20and%20published%20whatever%20they%20told%20him%20to%2C%20from%20the%20price%20target%20to%20what%20should%20and%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20the%20report.%20He%20asked%20them%20multiple%20times%20if%20they%20needed%20'more'.%20From%20what%20we%20can%20see%20in%20the%20dozens%20of%20exchanges%2C%20at%20no%20time%20did%20he%20have%20editorial%20control.%20He%20was%20being%20told%20what%20to%20publish%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20Frauds%20also%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20some%20email%20interactions%20-%20which%20it%20claims%20to%20have%20accessed%20through%20the%20documents%20available%20with%20the%20Ontario%20court%20-%20between%20Hindenburg%20and%20Anson%20to%20support%20its%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20multiple%20counts%20of%20securities%20fraud%20for%20both%20Anson%20Funds%20and%20Nate%20Anderson%2C%20and%20we%20have%20only%20gone%20through%205%20per%20cent%20of%20what's%20in%20there%20as%20of%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20what%20we%20have%20read%20so%20far%2C%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20certainty%20that%20when%20the%20whole%20exchange%20between%20Hindenburg%20and%20Anson%20reaches%20the%20SEC%2C%20Nate%20Anderson%20will%20be%20charged%20with%20securities%20fraud%20in%202025.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20association%20first%20emerged%2C%20Hindenburg%20had%20said%20it%20received%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20leads%20each%20year%20from%20diverse%20sources%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20industry%20experts%2C%20whistleblowers%20and%20other%20investors.%20%26quot%3BWe%20rigorously%20vet%20each%20lead%20and%20have%20always%20maintained%20full%20editorial%20independence%20over%20our%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Hindenburg%20Research%20published%20a%20report%20on%20Facedrive%2C%20a%20Canadian%20company%20that%20went%20public%20through%20a%20reverse%20merger%20as%20an%20eco-friendly%20ride-sharing%20service%2C%20chiding%20it%20for%20being%20over%20valued%20and%20lavishly%20paying%20promoters.%20Anson%20allegedly%20exchanged%20emails%20with%20Mr%20Anderson%20over%20the%20report%20and%20court%20documents%20reveal%20the%20hedge%20fund%20had%20knowledge%20of%20when%20the%20report%20was%20to%20be%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filings%20follow%20a%20separate%20years-long%20investigation%20by%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20and%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20In%20June%2C%20Anson%20Funds%20Management%20and%20Anson%20Advisors%20Inc%2C%20without%20admitting%20or%20denying%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%242.25%20million%20to%20settle%20SEC%20claims%20that%20they%20failed%20to%20tell%20clients%20about%20payments%20to%20outside%20publishers%20of%20bearish%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Mr%20Anderson%20announced%20the%20shutting%20down%20of%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20which%20made%20headlines%20globally%20in%202023%20after%20publishing%20reports%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20which%20refuted%20all%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20didn't%20share%20a%20specific%20reason%20for%20his%20decision%2C%20but%20expressed%20a%20desire%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNearly%20100%20individuals%20have%20been%20charged%20civilly%20or%20criminally%20by%20regulators%20at%20least%20in%20part%20through%20our%20work%2C%20including%20billionaires%20and%20oligarchs.%20We%20shook%20some%20empires%20that%20we%20felt%20needed%20shaking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20announcing%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737294960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fb5mtl5hg_nate-anderson-hindenburg_625x300_19_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhindenburgs-nate-anderson-under-cloud-over-alleged-links-with-hedge-fund-7509730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20short%20seller%20Nate%20Anderson%20who%20announced%20shutting%20down%20of%20his%20almost%20eight%20years%20old%20research%20firm%20Hindenburg%2C%20is%20under%20cloud%20for%20alleged%20links%20with%20hedge%20funds%20in%20preparing%20reports%20targeting%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhindenburgs-nate-anderson-under-cloud-over