20as%20she%20basked%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20winning%20the%20honour%2C%20the%2022-year-old%20ace%20shooter%20confirmed%20that%20the%20top%20layer%20of%20her%20medals%20had%20indeed%20peeled%20off%2C%20which%20seemed%20to%20have%20left%20her%20quite%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20last%20year%20had%20scripted%20history%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20She%20became%20the%20first-ever%20athlete%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20bad%20two%20medals%20in%20one%20edition%20of%20the%20quadrennial%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ace%20shooter%20opened%20India's%20medal%20tally%20in%20the%20Olympics%20after%20she%20secured%20third%20place%20in%20the%20women's%20individual%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%2C%20becoming%20the%20first-ever%20woman%20shooter%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20for%20India.%20Following%20that%2C%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20and%20Bhaker%20won%20the%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20(mixed%20team)%20event%2C%20which%20was%20India's%20first-ever%20shooting%20team%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20final%20event%2C%20she%20narrowly%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20historic%20grand%20treble%20and%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20women's%2025m%20pistol%20shooting%20event.%20She%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20opportunity%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20three%20medals%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737291120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdl59pkso_manu-bhaker-afp_625x300_25_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fshooting%2Fdouble-olympic-medallist-manu-bhakers-maternal-grandmother-uncle-die-in-haryana-road-accident-7510203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accident%20occurred%20on%20Mahendragarh%20bypass%20road%20in%20Charkhi%