icked%20up%20the%20broom%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20resumed%20her%20duty.%20I%20was%20quick%20to%20deduce%2C%20the%20hospital%20sweeper%20had%20just%20performed%20the%20delivery.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliving%20her%20first%20day%20at%20the%20Motihari%20District%20Hospital%20in%20Bihar%20gives%20Dr%20Taru%20Jindal%20the%20chills.%20Despite%20being%20briefed%20on%20the%20incongruities%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F16654%2Ftransform-defunct-rural-health-centre-model-facility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Bihar%20was%20once%20infamous%20for%20its%20high%20infant%20mortality%20rates%3B%2042%20deaths%20per%201%2C000%20live%20births%20before%202020%20%E2%80%94%20the%20young%20gynaecologist%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20expected%20the%20atrocities%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20outdo%20the%20theoretics%20to%20this%20degree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20she%20having%20second%20thoughts%20about%20leaving%20her%20cushy%20life%20in%20Mumbai%20in%202014%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20project%20in%20the%20hinterlands%3F%20%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reminisces.%20When%20she%20applied%20for%20the%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20sponsored%20by%20the%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%20and%20managed%20on%20the%20ground%20by%20two%20NGOs%2C%20%E2%80%98Care-India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Doctors%20For%20You%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20mandate%20was%20clear%3A%20use%20your%20medical%20prowess%20to%20train%20doctors%20in%20maternal%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%20Dr%20Taru%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20accounted%20for%20was%20the%20road%20to%20this%20go