l%20boost%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365338%2Fnagaland-institute-medical-sciences-research-nimsr-kohima-nagaland-dr-soumya-chakraborty-northeast-colleges%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emorale%20among%20medical%20students%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOptimal%20use%20of%20funds%20and%20ensuring%20accountability%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20used%20to%20think%20our%20rural%20hospitals%20suffered%20from%20lack%20of%20funds%2C%20and%20corruption%20led%20to%20further%20dilution%20of%20the%20available%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Taru%20shares.%20So%2C%20she%20was%20shocked%20when%20she%20learnt%20that%20every%20year%20Bihar%20sends%20back%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20PIP%20(Project%20Implementation%20Plan)%20%E2%80%94%20yearly%20funds%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20implement%20health%20schemes%20%E2%80%94%20funds%20unutilised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202017%2C%20Motihari%20had%20used%20only%2012%20percent%20of%20the%20funds%20sanctioned%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20learnt.%20The%20fallacy%20was%20rooted%20in%20an%20antiquated%20mindset.%20%E2%80%9CCorruption%20fear%20meant%20health%20officials%20were%20extremely%20reluctant%20to%20sanction%20money%20for%20anything.%20There%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20motivation%20to%20maintain%20records%2C%20which%20led%20to%20avoidance%20of%20using%20funds.%20Third%2C%20hospital%20managers%20are%20non-technical%20people%2C%20and%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20clear%20feedback%20from%20doctors%20and%20nurses%2C%20they%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20use%20much%20of%20the%20money%20obtained%20from%20these%20schemes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2