te%20items%20%3C%2Fa%3Einto%20useful%20products%20like%20public%20benches.%20While%203%2C000%20is%20just%20a%20small%20step%20toward%20the%20one-million%20goal%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20continuing%20our%20efforts%20until%20every%20piece%20of%20waste%20is%20addressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20also%20explored%20the%20B2B%20section%20to%20ensure%20the%20traceability%20and%20accountability%20of%20the%20plastic.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20focus%20on%20selling%20directly%20to%20the%20consumer%20because%2C%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20our%20accountability%20is%20lost.%20If%20something%20breaks%2C%20consumers%20will%20throw%20the%20furniture%20away%20and%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20back%20to%20us.%20With%20B2B%2C%20we%20can%20ensure%20proper%20traceability%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Alvin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDDemObyPZD9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDDemObyPZD9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDDemObyPZD9%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20targ