ttps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParai%20was%20considered%20as%20an%20instrument%20to%20be%20played%20by%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20lower%20caste%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nigar%20Kalai%20Koodam%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20association%20of%20the%20parai%20with%20alcohol%20significantly%20contributes%20to%20the%20social%20stigma%20surrounding%20its%20players.%20Playing%20the%20instrument%20requires%20immense%20energy%20and%20stamina%2C%20leading%20many%20players%20to%20submit%20to%20alcohol.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20alcohol%20was%20even%20used%20as%20a%20form%20of%20payment%20for%20parai%20players%2C%20further%20reinforcing%20this%20association.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20wear%20slippers%20or%20shirts%20when%20we%20played%20parai%2C%20which%20was%20frustrating%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manimaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20instrument%2C%20once%20a%20symbol%20of%20celebration%2C%20became%20a%20marker%20of%20social%20exclusion%20and%20systemic%20oppression%2C%20which%20the%20artists%20were%20not%20fond%20of.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20revolutionary%20protest%2C%20changing%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20parai%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiberation%20from%20the%20chains