0Pugalia%2C%20a%20class%2012%20student%20at%20Centre%20Point%20School%2C%20is%20driven%20by%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20help%20others.%20What%20started%20as%20tutoring%20a%20friend%20from%20a%20marginalised%20community%20soon%20uncovered%20a%20much%20larger%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20in%202022%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20help%20the%20son%20of%20a%20household%20maid%20with%20his%20studies.%20The%20boy%2C%20younger%20than%20Tejas%2C%20lived%20in%20a%20world%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20tutored%20him%2C%20I%20learnt%20about%20the%20struggles%20children%20face%20in%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20alarming%20issues%20I%20learnt%20was%20that%20many%20children%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20school%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20bags%20and%20their%20books%20would%20get%20ruined.%20Instead%2C%20some%20had%20to%20take%20up%20household%20chores%20or%20get%20involved%20in%20child%20labour%2C%20creating%20a%20gap%20in%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20was%20deeply%20moved%20as%20he%20realised%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20school%20bag%20was%20preventing%20children%20in%20government%20schools%20from%20continuing%20their%20education%20during%20monsoons.%20It%20was%20a%20problem%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20solve%20sustainably.%20With%20his%20curiosity%20piqued%20and%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20helping%2C%20he%20thought%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20upcycling%20textile%20waste%2C%20a%20serious%20environmental%20issue%2C%20and%20using%20it%20to%20